{"tid":1575064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警？毅進仔？有冇諗過「香港警察」四個字先最震撼？","createTime":"2019-09-16T16:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T16:43:07.000Z","uid":233929,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ea421236bfeebbca982a516c31d8f2f37cdfae","tid":1575064,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"如果你係陳大文<br />\n係條街最怕比人點叫？<br />\n大文？肥文？死肥文？<br />\n錯，係全名陳大文呀！<br />\n<br />\n心理學有講過，被叫全名既人反應會最快最激烈。<br />\n同樣道理，<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「香港警察」唔會承認自己係死黑警，毅進仔，黑社會。但佢地心入面冇得否認自己係「香港警察」。</span></span><br />\n呢下係全名外最能比到壓力同侮辱佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我建議所有文宣/屌狗都應該加入「香港警察」四個字，減低佢地認受性，醜化「香港警察」呢職業，令「香港警察」四個字永久變成污名！<br />\n令佢地世世代代永不超生！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：屌狗個時當然黑警，毅進仔屌得順口，亦唔係叫你地唔用，<br />\n但大家可以試下間中插幾句「香港警察，狗屎垃圾」<br />\n「香港警察，落地獄死全家」，「屌你老母，香港警察」<br />\n「香港警察，吞精口爆」etc 自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n在此，以正「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察</span></span>」視聽！"},{"pid":"2880874e153505359cea4c35b449d2ecba8cff70","tid":1575064,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jR5wr1.jpg&h=d9b2c693&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcddf0b3380da989e4e5ebe9efc3c6577f90af1a","tid":1575064,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbicfVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbicfVy.png&h=be800046&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a934270cb0009bc73e0442912ab885e71e2b51e","tid":1575064,"uid":233929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":